headline: SJM Q2 Earnings Miss Despite Higher Sales, FY26 Guidance Tightened
summary: SJM's Q2 shows rising sales but a steep earnings slump, prompting tightened FY26 guidance as pricing gains clash with softer volumes and higher costs.

headline: Smucker (SJM) Q2 Earnings Lag Estimates
summary: Smucker (SJM) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -0.94% and +0.34%, respectively, for the quarter ended October 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
